							<td colspan=2><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">LDoN and so many other factors have fragmented Guilds and seem to be depleting the number of  players available for raids. Many casual Guilds are having trouble raiding, yet we all want to ultimately reach the high end game, get to the Plane of Time.<br><br>

A few far thinking Guild Leaders have formed ZebCon, a Confederation of Guilds to do just that. We have had some minor raids so far and as we finalize loot rules and overcome other possible obsticles.  We expect more  Guilds to join and maybe even some of the larger guilds on our server.<br><br> 

The concept is to form a pool of players wanting to raid who can do so, while staying in their own Guild, with their friends.  Working along side other trained, qualified people in a fun friendly controlled atmosphere to raid. <br><br>

